<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edit Area Konservasi</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        #background-video {
            position: fixed;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            min-height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #006994, #003366);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .header-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo-svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #66ccff;
        }

        /* Main Content Styles */
        main {
            margin-top: 80px;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 160px);
            padding: 2rem 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            animation: titleFadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes titleFadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        form {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 105, 148, 0.9), rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.9));
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: formSlideUp 0.8s ease-out;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        @keyframes formSlideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="number"],
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus,
        input[type="number"]:focus,
        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #66ccff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(102, 204, 255, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        textarea {
            height: 150px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        button[type="submit"] {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #66ccff, #003366);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            width: 100%;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes buttonGlow {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            animation: buttonGlow 3s linear infinite;
            background-size: 200% auto;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: #66ccff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Footer Styles */
        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #003366, #006994);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .footer-section h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .footer-section p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #66ccff;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .bottom-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .footer-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .social-links {
                justify-content: center;
            }

            form {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            input[type="text"],
            input[type="number"],
            textarea {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            label {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <video autoplay muted loop id="background-video">
        <source src="/public/19016098-hd_1920_1080_30fps.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>

    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo-container">
                <svg class="logo-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M10,50 Q25,40 40,50 T70,50 T100,50" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M10,65 Q25,55 40,65 T70,65 T100,65" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M60,35 Q70,25 80,35 L85,30 L85,40 L80,35 Q70,45 60,35" fill="white"/>
                    <circle cx="30" cy="25" r="5" fill="white"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="logo-text">InfoSea</span>
            </a>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Beranda</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/species">Daftar Spesies</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/conservation">Area Konservasi</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/participation">Partisipasi</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/auth/login">Login</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h1>Edit Area Konservasi</h1>
        <form action="/conservation/edit/<%= area.id %>" method="POST">
            <label for="name">Nama Area:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" value="<%= area.name %>" required>

            <label for="location">Lokasi:</label>
            <input type="text" id="location" name="location" value="<%= area.location %>" required>

            <label for="area_size">Ukuran Area (kmÂ²):</label>
            <input type="number" id="area_size" name="area_size" step="0.01" value="<%= area.area_size %>" required>

            <label for="description">Deskripsi:</label>
            <textarea id="description" name="description"><%= area.description %></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Perbarui Area</button>
        </form>
        <a href="/conservation" class="back-link">Kembali ke Daftar Area Konservasi</a>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Tentang InfoSea</h3>
                <p>InfoSea adalah platform edukasi yang didedikasikan untuk melestarikan dan mengedukasi masyarakat tentang kekayaan laut Indonesia.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Kontak</h3>
                <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> info@infosea.id</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> (021) 1234-5678</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Jakarta, Indonesia</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Ikuti Kami</h3>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="YouTube"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 InfoSea. Dibuat Oleh Fadli Kurnia Ramadhan</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const form = document.querySelector('form');
            const inputs = form.querySelectorAll('input, textarea');
            
            inputs.forEach(input => {
                input.addEventListener('focus', function() {
                    this.style.transform = 'translateY(-2px)';
                });
                
                input.addEventListener('blur', function() {
                    this.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>